  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Regular pickup is a benefit of BackShip. You can schedule a shipping provider to pick up packages daily at your chosen time and location.<br><br><strong>Benefits</strong></span></p>\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">No more drop offs at collection points</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">More time for quality testing</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Improve your On-Time Delivery rate</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">No additional costs</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"> <img alt=\"Backship 1.png\" src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0Sb0000007P9l&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EM3X000009giRP\"></img></span><br> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Which shipping providers are available and what are their requirements for regular pickups?</strong></span><br><br> </p>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Shipping provider</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Regular pickup available</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">DHL Express</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">YES</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">1 package / day</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">UPS (standard and express)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">YES</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">1 package / day</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Correos Express</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">YES</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">1 package / day</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Chronopost</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">YES</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Minimum 3 packages / day</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">DPD UK</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">YES</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Minimum 100 packages / month</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">DPD DE</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">YES</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Minimum 100 packages / month</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Colissimo</span></td><td colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">No regular pickup yet</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p> </p>\n<h3 style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>How do I set up a recurring regular pickup?</strong></span></h3>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"> </p>\n<div style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Submit a support request via the Seller Support Center by following these steps:</span></div>\n<ol><li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Is the question order related? &gt; No</span></li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">What does your question concern? &gt; Back Market services</span></li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Which service &gt; BackShip</span></li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">What do you want to do? &gt; Set up a regular pickup</span></li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Click on the link to fill in your request and then submit it</span></li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Wait until our team gets back to you shortly</span></li></ol>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><br><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Setting up regular BackShip pickups usually takes approximately 7 business days.</span></p>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>About automatic API call to shipping providers</strong><br><br>With DHL Express, Correos Express, and UPS, once you confirm an order, this integration automatically schedules a pickup with the shipping provider for the next business day. To modify a pickup or inform us about a shipping provider that failed to pick up your packages, <u><strong><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/submit-new-request\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #3498db;\">submit a support request via the Seller Support Center </span></a>.</strong></u><br><br><br><img alt=\"Backship 2.png\" src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0Sb0000007P9l&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EM3X000009giT6\"></img></span></p>"
}